---
layout: layouts/base.njk
pageLayout: inner
showLoader: false
showRail: false
---
<section class="chapter chapter--light news-list-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <nav class="breadcrumb news-list-hero__crumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="{{ '/' | url }}">
        <span class="lang en">{{ i18n.en.breadcrumbHome }}</span>
        <span class="lang vi">{{ i18n.vi.breadcrumbHome }}</span>
        <span class="lang zh">{{ i18n.zh.breadcrumbHome }}</span>
      </a>
      <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
      <span>
        <span class="lang en">News</span>
        <span class="lang vi">Tin tức</span>
        <span class="lang zh">新闻</span>
      </span>
    </nav>
    <header class="chapter__head">
      <span class="chapter__num reveal">11</span>
      <p class="eyebrow reveal">
        <span class="lang en">News</span>
        <span class="lang vi">Tin tức</span>
        <span class="lang zh">新闻</span>
      </p>
      <h1 class="chapter__title">
        <span class="lang en">
          <span class="line-mask"><span class="line">What’s Happening</span></span>
          <span class="line-mask"><span class="line line--muted">at Nam Viet.</span></span>
        </span>
        <span class="lang vi">
          <span class="line-mask"><span class="line">Tin mới</span></span>
          <span class="line-mask"><span class="line line--muted">từ Nam Việt.</span></span>
        </span>
        <span class="lang zh">
          <span class="line-mask"><span class="line">南越</span></span>
          <span class="line-mask"><span class="line line--muted">最新动态。</span></span>
        </span>
      </h1>
      <p class="chapter__desc reveal" data-delay="200">
        <span class="lang en">Project updates, business activities and key developments across the Nam Viet ecosystem.</span>
        <span class="lang vi">Cập nhật dự án, hoạt động doanh nghiệp và những diễn biến đáng chú ý trong hệ sinh thái Nam Việt.</span>
        <span class="lang zh">了解南越的项目进展、企业动态与重要更新。</span>
      </p>
    </header>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="inner-body news-list-body">
  <div class="container">
{{ content | safe }}
  </div>
</section>
